data.name: label13.Text
data.value: If You Have an Issue or Want To Report a Book, Feel Free To Contact Our Staff Team (The Button Below) and They Will Help You Solve Your Problem. We Are Interested To Have Your Feedback. Thank You For Choosing Us!

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Return The Book Back To The Library Before Its Deadline Date to NOT Lose Points ( Check The Return Date Of Your Book In Our Page ). If You Fail to Return The Books, You Will Be Prohibited From Borrowing and Will Be Permanently Added Into Our Blacklist.
